Reminiscent of a fine Spanish estate or resort, the new master planned community, Estancia Del Sol will consist of 91 assisted living and 21 memory care apartments in an atmosphere that radiates comfortable yet elegant surroundings. Estancia Del Sol‚Äôs timeline for development is approximately 15 months. With ground breaking planned in November 2013, construction is slated to be complete early 2015.

‚ÄúEstancia Del Sol will bring a hospitality and boutique feel that will redefine senior living ‚Äì a philosophy like this may not be what you‚Äôd expect from senior living, but we imagine seniors living in Corona will enjoy getting used to it.‚Äù Says Patrick Collins, Vice President of Operations.

Estancia Del Sol will be designed with Spanish influence and many high end amenities and innovative programs. Residents will enjoy spacious private apartments, full-service fine dining, theatre, spa, fitness center, transportation, engaging activities, expansive landscape and full access to exceptional personal care or concierge services as needed.

WESTliving understands the need for a continuum of care model and responds by designing Estancia Del Sol to accommodate all stages of an individual‚Äôs needs. From active and engaging activities, beauty/spa treatments, innovative wellness and fitness programs, residents are lavished with the attention they deserve. For residents who need a little hand now and then, personalized care services are available including; special diets, medication supervision, ambulation assistance, medical appointments, bathing, dressing and personal grooming assistance or escorts to meals and activities. The Renaissance memory care environment will be specifically designed to reinforce safety and comfort for residents with Alzheimer‚Äôs or other related dementias. The memory care program brings a therapeutic, holistic approach to care with a focus on meaningful connections and life-enriching experiences for residents every day.

<h3>About WESTliving</h3>

WESTliving was formed in early 2009 to own and operate hospitality based senior living communities providing an exceptional variety of lifestyles, wellness, and care options. Located in Carlsbad, California, WESTliving owns and operates within the Pacific and Southwest regions of the United States. From independent living through assisted living, WESTliving combines comfortable elegance with attentive, world-class service, the result? A true sense of belonging for seniors and their families. Find out what senior living was meant to be. More information about WESTliving can be found at <a href="http://www.WESTliving.net">www.WESTliving.net</a>.";s:10:"post_title";s:70:"Corona Welcomes WESTliving's Newest Senior Community: Estancia Del Sol";s:12:"post_excerpt";s:303:"WESTliving, an owner and operator of hospitality based senior living communities, unveils its plans to build an independent, assisted living and memory care community offering a world-class residential senior housing community located in the newest up-scale area of South Corona, CA in Riverside County.";s:11:"post_status";s:7:"publish";s:14:"comment_status";s:4:"open";s:11:"ping_status";s:6:"closed";s:13:"post_password";s:0:"";s:9:"post_name";s:32:"corona-welcomes-estancia-del-sol";s:7:"to_ping";s:0:"";s:6:"pinged";s:0:"";s:13:"post_modified";s:19:"2014-08-25 16:54:01";s:17:"post_modified_gmt";s:19:"2014-08-25 16:54:01";s:21:"post_content_filtered";s:0:"";s:11:"post_parent";s:1:"0";s:4:"guid";s:32:"http://new.westliving.net/?p=102";s:10:"menu_order";s:1:"0";s:9:"post_type";s:4:"post";s:14:"post_mime_type";s:0:"";s:13:"comment_count";s:1:"0";}i:1;O:8:"stdClass":23:{s:2:"ID";s:3:"208";s:11:"post_author";s:1:"3";s:9:"post_date";s:19:"2014-08-25 16:00:44";s:13:"post_date_gmt";s:19:"2014-08-25 16:00:44";s:12:"post_content";s:2880:"<strong>CORONA, CA (August 25, 2014)</strong> Estancia Del Sol, WESTliving‚Äôs newest senior living community is pleased to announce the opening of their Leasing Center.  The Leasing Center is open 7 days a week from 9:00 a.m. to 5:00 p.m. and welcomes prospective residents and families to drop by for a glimpse of the exceptional lifestyle, amenities and innovative programs Estancia Del Sol has to offer.  This new development broke ground in November 2013, and is slated to be complete in December 2014.

‚ÄúInterest level has exceeded expectations‚Äù, says Carrie Compton, sales director.  ‚ÄúThe Marketing team is already taking reservations for preferred locations.  And a sneak preview ‚ÄúDusty Shoe‚Äù event will be scheduled in September for the general public.‚Äù

Reminiscent of a fine Spanish estate, the new master planned community, Estancia Del Sol will consist of 91 assisted living and 26 memory care apartments.  The community is conveniently located with easy freeway access and is in close proximity to many shopping amenities.

‚ÄúWhile the opening of the building itself is scheduled for December of this year, one can already see the elegant design of the apartments and superior construction workmanship,‚Äù says General Manager Sam Faye. ‚ÄúWe are very proud of our newly built ‚Äúflagship‚Äù community.‚Äù

Estancia Del Sol is a private-pay community with monthly fees starting at $2,650 per month. The monthly fee includes three daily chef-prepared meals, weekly housekeeping and linen service, transportation, and engaging activities including exercise classes in the fitness center, and 24 hour staffing.

‚ÄúEstancia Del Sol will bring a hospitality and boutique feel that will redefine senior living ‚Äì a philosophy like this may not be what you‚Äôd expect from senior living, but we imagine seniors living in Corona will enjoy getting used to it.‚Äù says Patrick Collins, vice president of operations.

<h3>About WESTliving</h3>

WESTliving was formed in early 2009 to own and operate hospitality based senior living communities providing an exceptional variety of lifestyles, wellness, and care options. Located in Carlsbad, California, WESTliving owns and operates within the Pacific and Southwest regions of the United States. From independent living through assisted living, WESTliving combines comfortable elegance with attentive, world-class service, the result? A true sense of belonging for seniors and their families. Find out what senior living was meant to be. More information about WESTliving can be found at <a href="http://www.WESTliving.net">www.WESTliving.net</a>.

